abstract: Before E*Trade Financial agreed to a deal with the Citadel Investment Group, the hedge fund run by Kenneth C. Griffith, a parade of almost 40 other suitors had come calling.
lead_paragraph: Before E*Trade Financial agreed to a deal with the Citadel Investment Group, the hedge fund run by Kenneth C. Griffith, a parade of almost 40 other suitors had come calling.

headline.main: E*Trade: Before the Citadel Deal, a Parade of Suitors
